<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; }
        nav { background: #333; color: white; padding: 15px 0; position: sticky; top: 0; }
        nav a { color: white; margin: 0 20px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
        nav a:hover { color: #4CAF50; }
        main { max-width: 1000px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 20px; background: white; border-radius: 8px; }
        h1 { color: #333; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        p { color: #666; line-height: 1.6; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
     <nav>
        <a href="/">🏠 Home</a>
        <a href="/servicos">🛁 Serviços</a>
        <a href="/pets">🐾 Pets</a>
        <a href="/users">👥 Usuários</a>
        <a href="/agendamentos">📅 Agendamentos</a>
        <button onclick="logout()">Sair</button>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <p>Bem-vindo ao sistema de gestão de usuários e pets!</p>
        <p>Clique em "Usuários" ou "Pets" para gerenciar.</p>
    </main>
</body>
</html>